SFFG 120 
(formerly FRM 120) Environmental and Natural Resource Worldviews (3)  
Introduction to the philosophical dimensions of human-habitat relationships; Western, Oriental, and indigenous Filipino worldviews about the environment and forests; and political-economic dimensions of environmentalism within the realities of Philippine society  
3 hrs (class)  
PR. PHLO 1 and SOSC II or COI  
(1,2) 
